{"tid":292421,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖慎入，正式宣告秋葵屎先係屎中極品","createTime":"2017-06-21T11:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T01:13:11.000Z","uid":115,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e625267fc9c41be32bf7bb892f0ff3c64a7a9fd6","tid":292421,"uid":115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"呢排行過街市，口多多問下阿姐有咩當造<br />\n阿姐話初夏既秋葵最靚，有益健康 又乜又染<br />\n好似仲話咩食左碌鳩識轉彎<br />\n我份人又冇咩所謂，見阿姐落足嘴頭<br />\n平平地咁買左$20，已經有一大堆<br />\n<br />\n番到屋企就好似煮菜咁，加鹽加油 淥佢一陣<br />\n再整多個酸辣醬汁，加多枝大青島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一邊R住肚腩，一邊睇愛回家<br />\n<br />\n第一次食秋葵，又幾過癮<br />\n淡淡清新瓜味，口感幾爽<br />\n而且入面d籽幾有口感<br />\n但尾部 尖端有點苦<br />\n切開會有少少黏液，應該是精華黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知半夜訓訓下極肚痛<br />\n未落床已經痛到彎哂身<br />\n好彩屋企細，但到廁所門口已經feel到括約筋抽蓄<br />\n即是二邊屎忽係咁震<br />\n一除條褲 就好似跑馬咁，d屎係咁衝出黎<br />\n爽撚到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成件事唔洗二分鐘<br />\n感覺個肚好空虛<br />\n但係個人聰明左，行路又快<br />\n好似係<br />\n最緊要發現到d屎有一粒粒白色秋葵籽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/191639_bb55a81ac498789d4e9d8371ddb36280.jpg[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F191639_bb55a81ac498789d4e9d8371ddb36280.jpg%5Bimg%5D&d=ISdeuin%2BCt4GA%2BY9SdWPfsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=a8fe7a48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/191639_bb55a81ac498789d4e9d8371ddb36280.jpg[img]</a><br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/191640_1c4a582dd083fb816345b63fb05381b4.jpg[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F191640_1c4a582dd083fb816345b63fb05381b4.jpg%5Bimg%5D&d=ISdeuin%2BCt4GA%2BY9SdWPfsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=bfdccf96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/191640_1c4a582dd083fb816345b63fb05381b4.jpg[img]</a>"},{"pid":"8a76411e94010fdeb7b4837c58a0f67daa4862a0","tid":292421,"uid":115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:17:49.000Z","msg":"[img.]<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/191735_ff38aa3485e7d44a4a87bb8638e6da02.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F191735_ff38aa3485e7d44a4a87bb8638e6da02.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=ISdeuin%2BCt4GA%2BY9SdWPfsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=aec4a614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/191735_ff38aa3485e7d44a4a87bb8638e6da02.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n[img.]<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/191736_3000b54a05a6268325022a9296da8500.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F191736_3000b54a05a6268325022a9296da8500.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=ISdeuin%2BCt4GA%2BY9SdWPfsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=f20b707b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/191736_3000b54a05a6268325022a9296da8500.jpg[/img]</a>"},{"pid":"86347764099942ac75dbda7c02a7f52ddcca1601","tid":292421,"uid":115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:18:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/191818_a1d5e97b776cd3f8227ff5ae220d6ca6.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F191818_a1d5e97b776cd3f8227ff5ae220d6ca6.jpg&d=ISdeuin%2BCt4GA%2BY9SdWPfsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=121e8aea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/191818_a1d5e97b776cd3f8227ff5ae220d6ca6.